# Real APKs used for local dev-time parser verification. Never commit a
# third party's binary to this repo — see testdata/real/README.md for how
# to fetch one on demand.
/testdata/real/*.apk

# Build output
/mobilegate
/dist/

# Local baseline files written during ad hoc/manual testing. A project
# adopting baseline mode commits its OWN .mobilegate-baseline.yml
# deliberately (see README) — this ignore is for scratch runs against
# whatever APK happens to be lying around locally, not a statement that
# baseline files in general shouldn't be tracked.
/.mobilegate-baseline.yml

# Claude Code's local session state (permission allowlist, absolute
# local paths) — machine-specific, never meant to ship. Was previously
# only excluded via this machine's global gitignore, which doesn't
# travel with the repo; listed explicitly here so a fresh clone doesn't
# pick it up either.
.claude/

# Editor/IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# macOS
.DS_Store
